  "pitch": "A quirky platformer following young Timmy's quest for justice. Unique mechanics, colorful worlds, and boss battles await in this charming adventure.",
  "description": "When Timmy's favorite toy is stolen by the neighborhood bully, he embarks on an epic quest through imaginative worlds born from a child's imagination. Timmy's Revenge is a heartwarming platformer that combines classic jump-and-run gameplay with innovative mechanics like emotion-based abilities and perspective-shifting puzzles. Each world represents different aspects of childhood, from the backyard jungle gym to the mysterious basement."
